c: 3
v: 55
t: "Yeroo Rabbiin jedhes [yaadadhu]:[] “Yaa Iisaa! Ani si raffisaadhaGara kiyyattis ol si fuudhaadhaIsaan kafaran irraas si qulqulleessaadhaIsaan si hordofanis hanga Guyyaa Qiyaamatti warra kafaran irratti ol taasisaadhaErgasii deebiin keessan gara kiyya; waan isin isa keessatti wal dhabaa turtan keessattis gidduu keessanitti nan murteessa"